article.description: — Ocypher Owens scored 26 points as Le Moyne beat Houghton 92-72 on Monday night.
article.headline: Owens scores 26, Le Moyne knocks off Houghton 92-72
article.linkText: Owens scores 26, Le Moyne knocks off Houghton 92-72
article.story: SYRACUSE, N.Y. -- — Ocypher Owens scored 26 points as Le Moyne beat Houghton 92-72 on Monday night. Owens added five rebounds for the Dolphins (5-7). Kaiyem Cleary scored 19 points while going 7 of 12 (3 for 3 from 3-point range), and added five rebounds. Isaiah Salter had 15 points and was 6 of 10 shooting (3 for 7 from 3-point range). Jajuan Preaster led the way for the Highlanders with 17 points and seven assists. Houghton also got 15 points and six rebounds from Preston Thomas. Aaron Johnson also put up 12 points and six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
